metadata.name: me n who
metadata.description:
me n who,  
digital image manipulation,  
1016 px X 1224 px,  
2023,

This work is part of a series further exploring the memetics I became aware of during the creation of works for the Post-Internet Consciousness collection. 

All images used are either viral memes or viral images that have ended up on my various social media timelines. They are then edited and manipulated by me how I see fit. The aim of this series is to further explore memetics in all of its aspects, from the simple aspects of a nonsensical images going viral to the none attribution, copy, paste, and steal aspects.
